# DEBIAN/templates

Template: ophelia-ci/server-port
Type: integer
Default: 50051
Description: Ophelia CI server port:
 Enter the port number for the Ophelia CI server.

Template: ophelia-ci/db-path
Type: string
Default: "/var/lib/ophelia/ophelia.db"
Description: Ophelia CI database path:
 Enter the path to the Ophelia CI database file.

Template: ophelia-ci/expiration-time
Type: integer
Default: 30
Description: Ophelia CI token expiration time (days):
 Enter the token expiration time in days.

Template: ophelia-ci/secret
Type: string
Default: ""
Description: Ophelia CI server secret:
 Enter the server secret (leave empty for auto-generation).

Template: ophelia-ci/ssl-cert-file
Type: string
Default: ""
Description: SSL certificate file path:
 Enter the path to the SSL certificate file (leave empty for no SSL).

Template: ophelia-ci/ssl-key-file
Type: string
Default: ""
Description: SSL key file path:
 Enter the path to the SSL key file (leave empty for no SSL).

Template: ophelia-ci/update-config
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Update existing configuration?
 Do you want to update the existing configuration file?